<section class="case-study__section--white case-study--background">
	<div class="wrapper">
		<h2>Background</h2>
		<div class="row cf">
			<div class="col3"></div>
			<div class="col7">
				<p>Buildcloud is a kick ass technology start-up based in Leeds. They had a vision to create a cloud based project managment tool for architects, which we helped transform from a cool idea into a real product.</p>
				<p>We worked with the Buildcloud founders to design and build an app that revolutionises how architects manage &amp; communicate on projects.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col2"></div>
		</div><!--end row-->
	</div>
</section>

<section class="case-study__section--grey case-study--design">
	<div class="wrapper">
		<h2>Design</h2>
		<div class="row cf">
			
			<div class="design-txt">
				<p>At its heart Buildcloud is about information &amp; communication so the design needed to put this to the fore. The interface was kept clean, clear and simple with a minimal core colour pallet. Subtle animations where used to provide greater context when interacting with the user interface.</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="overlay ipad-overlay">
				<%= image_tag 'IPAD.svg', :alt => "Ipad" %>
